 I apologize for the error in my previous response. Here is an updated version of the XML file without any errors:
```php
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<mission xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
    <title>Orchard Robotic Mission Plan</title>
    <description>This is a sample mission plan to measure cos and co2 of trees in an orchard.</description>
    
    <!-- Start Position -->
    <position id="start">
        <x>0.0000000</x>
        <y>0.0000000</y>
        <z>0.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Middle Position -->
    <position id="middle">
        <x>2.0000000</x>
        <y>2.0000000</y>
        <z>2.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Co2 and Cos Position -->
    <position id="co2_cos">
        <x>4.0000000</x>
        <y>4.0000000</y>
        <z>4.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Northern Position -->
    <position id="northern">
        <x>6.0000000</x>
        <y>0.0000000</y>
        <z>0.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Temperature Position -->
    <position id="temperature">
        <x>8.0000000</x>
        <y>0.0000000</y>
        <z>0.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Return Position -->
    <position id="return">
        <x>0.0000000</x>
        <y>0.0000000</y>
        <z>0.0000000</z>
    </position>
    
    <!-- Tasks -->
    <task id="cos">
        <description>Measure cos at the middle position.</description>
        <equipment id="cos_sensor">Cos Sensor</equipment>
        <action>Take a reading using the Cos Sensor.</action>
        <condition>If the reading is low, proceed to take 2 pictures of nearby trees.</condition>
    </task>
    
    <task id="cos_pictures">
        <description>Take 2 pictures of nearby trees at the middle position.</description>
        <equipment id="camera">Camera</equipment>
        <action>Take a picture using the Camera.</action>
    </task>
    
    <task id="co2">
        <description>Measure co2 at the co2 and cos position.</description>
        <equipment id="co2_sensor">Co2 Sensor</equipment>
        <action>Take a reading using the Co2 Sensor.</action>
    </task>
    
    <!-- Move to next task -->
    <move from="start" to="middle"/>
    
    <!-- Move to next task -->
    <move from="middle" to="co2_cos"/>
    
    <!-- Move to next task -->
    <move from="co2_cos" to="northern"/>
    
    <!-- Move back to start -->
    <move from="temperature" to="return"/>
</mission>
```
This XML file has corrected the `xsi:schema-instance` attribute and added a task for taking 2 pictures of nearby trees at the middle position. I have also modified the description for the cos measurement task, and changed the equipment name for the co2 measurement task to "Co2 Sensor". You can adjust the positions, equipment, tasks, and actions as needed to fit your specific requirements. 